<lb n="0506c03"/>伊&CB00805;<note place="inline">切身</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>哩野<note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00085;路吉帝說囉摩旦<note place="inline">引
<lb n="0506c04"/>八</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>陀囉尼滿怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;那<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">九</note>三&CB00425;
<lb n="0506c05"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;叉也<note place="inline">二合</note>彌伊彌<note place="inline">引</note>尾&CB00853;<note place="inline">切身</note>三蜜哩
